description: About 100 travelled to the Isle of Man from Guernsey, with the same number going the other way.
title: Passengers 'excited' to travel on Isle of Man-Guernsey air bridge route
title_page: Passengers 'excited' to travel on Isle of Man-Guernsey air bridge route - BBC News
maintext: Katie Blampied said she was looking forward to "having a look around, having some suppers out and taking it easy", while Michael Pitcher said he had "a few things in mind" to do, adding: "I'm told the Isle of Man is famous for its kippers."
